	highlight the scope of the review in general\, set expected timelines\, li
	st of initial requirements (see attached Engagement Memorandum) and answer
	 any queries you might have.<o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp
	\;</o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal">Thanks\,<o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNorma
